Description of problem: Tried to put root partition on iSCSI disk in blivet-gui. Selected iSCSI device, added new partition, put "/" as mountpoint, clicked on "OK".
Version-Release number of selected component: anaconda-26.21.6-1
The following was filed automatically by anaconda: anaconda 26.21.6-1 exception report Traceback (most recent call first): File "/usr/lib/python3.6/site-packages/blivetgui/blivet_utils.py", line 1134, in add_device add_function = self.add_dict[user_input.device_type] File "/usr/lib/python3.6/site-packages/blivetgui/osinstall.py", line 78, in remote_call return utils_method(*args) File "/usr/lib/python3.6/site-packages/blivetgui/blivetgui.py", line 442, in add_device result = self.client.remote_call("add_device", user_input) KeyError: None
Additional info: addons: com_redhat_docker, com_redhat_kdump cmdline: /usr/libexec/system-python /sbin/anaconda executable: /sbin/anaconda hashmarkername: anaconda kernel: 4.11.0-2.fc26.x86_64 product: Fedora release: Cannot get release name. type: anaconda version: 26
blivet-gui-2.1.5-1.fc26 has been submitted as an update to Fedora 26. https://bodhi.fedoraproject.org/updates/FEDORA-2017-4fa8dcbca7
